
Codebook

Data Information

Original data: https://d396qusza40orc.cloudfront.net/getdata%2Fprojectfiles%2FUCI%20HAR%20Dataset.zip <br>
Original description of the dataset: http://archive.ics.uci.edu/ml/datasets/Human+Activity+Recognition+Using+Smartphones

<p style="font-size:20px"> Script Detail </p>

Merges the training and the test sets to create one data set. <br>
Extracts only the measurements on the mean and standard deviation for each measurement. <br>
Uses descriptive activity names to name the activities in the data set <br>
Appropriately labels the data set with descriptive activity names. <br>
Creates a second, independent tidy data set with the average of each variable for each activity and each subject. <br>


<p style="font-size:20px"> Script Function </p>

Load librairies dplyr and stringr <br>
Load all data and create objects <br>
Rename Columns for test and train (separately) to make data tidy <br>
Rename Activity Labels for test and train <br>
Create object that combines all test and all train data <br>
Merge both datasets
Create new dataset of the mean of each variable for each activity and each subject

